context:
KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;돌아와, 히스.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;Come back, Heath.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;보랏빛 꽃만이 유일한 아름다움으로 남아있는 그 저택으로.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;To the manor where the last vestiges of its beauty remain in its violet flowers.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;폭풍으로 뚫린 균열 사이로 모든 온기가 빠져나갔던 그 저택으로.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;To the manor where its storm-broken breach
has siphoned all that was once warm.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;너에게 삶을 내어준 대신 모멸감과 무너짐을 안겨주었던 그 저택으로.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;To the manor that gave you not only life...
but also scorn and desolation.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;난롯불 가운데가 아닌 차가운 모퉁이 어귀만이 네 자리였던 그 저택으로.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;To the manor where your place was the frozen corner
that couldn't be further from the hearth.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;황야에서 돌아와.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;Return from the moors.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;이제 집으로 올 시간이야.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#4e3076&gt;It’s time for you to come home.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;여기가 T사 둥지구나…&gt;
EN:
&lt;So this is what T Corp.’s Nest looks like...&gt;

KR:
&lt;워더링하이츠라는 이름의 저택이 다음 목적지였다고 했지?&gt;
EN:
&lt;We’re headed to this place called ‘Wuthering Heights’ next, right?&gt;

KR:
&lt;갱단에도 버러지 같은 게 있고 아닌 게 있어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;… There are gangs that aren’t scummy?&gt;
